Rayman Mini collects data for game saves, achievements and leaderboards and stores it on Apple services such as iCloud and Game Center. If you decline to have your data stored in iCloud and Game Center, you will only be able to play offline and you won’t participate in leaderboards.
We don’t store personal or gameplay data on our servers. We have limited our data collection and use practices to customer support actions.
This data policy applies to kids. Parents can request deletion of data by writing to Ubisoft customer support at
https://support.ubisoft.com/Article/000063467/
.